17#ifndef RDATA_IN_1_A6_28_C
18#define RDATA_IN_1_A6_28_C

20#include <isc/net.h>

22#define RRTYPE_A6_ATTRIBUTES (0)

24static inline isc_result_t
25fromtext_in_a6(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
26 isc_token_t token;
27 unsigned char addr[16];
28 unsigned char prefixlen;
29 unsigned char octets;
30 unsigned char mask;
31 dns_name_t name;
32 isc_buffer_t buffer;
33 bool ok;
34
35 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_a6);
36 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
37
38 UNUSED(type);
39 UNUSED(rdclass);
40 UNUSED(callbacks);
41
42 /*
43 * Prefix length.
44 */
45 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
46 false));
47 if (token.value.as_ulong > 128U)
48 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
49
50 prefixlen = (unsigned char)token.value.as_ulong;
51 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, &prefixlen, 1));
52
53 /*
54 * Suffix.
55 */
56 if (prefixlen != 128) {
57 /*
58 * Prefix 0..127.
59 */
60 octets = prefixlen/8;
61 /*
62 * Octets 0..15.
63 */
64 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token,
65 isc_tokentype_string,
66 false));
67 if (inet_pton(AF_INET6, DNS_AS_STR(token), addr) != 1)
68 RETTOK(DNS_R_BADAAAA);
69 mask = 0xff >> (prefixlen % 8);
70 addr[octets] &= mask;
71 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, &addr[octets], 16 - octets));
72 }
73
74 if (prefixlen == 0)
75 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
76
77 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
78 false));
79 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
80 buffer_fromregion(&buffer, &token.value.as_region);
81 if (origin == NULL)
82 origin = dns_rootname;
83 RETTOK(dns_name_fromtext(&name, &buffer, origin, options, target));
84 ok = true;
85 if ((options & DNS_RDATA_CHECKNAMES) != 0)
86 ok = dns_name_ishostname(&name, false);
87 if (!ok && (options & DNS_RDATA_CHECKNAMESFAIL) != 0)
88 RETTOK(DNS_R_BADNAME);
89 if (!ok && callbacks != NULL)
90 warn_badname(&name, lexer, callbacks);
91 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
92}

94static inline isc_result_t
95totext_in_a6(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
96 isc_region_t sr, ar;
97 unsigned char addr[16];
98 unsigned char prefixlen;
99 unsigned char octets;
100 unsigned char mask;
101 char buf[sizeof("128")];
102 dns_name_t name;
103 dns_name_t prefix;
104 bool sub;
105
106 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_a6);
107 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
108 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
109
110 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
111 prefixlen = sr.base[0];
112 INSIST(prefixlen <= 128);
113 isc_region_consume(&sr, 1);
114 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u", prefixlen);
115 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
116 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
117
118 if (prefixlen != 128) {
119 octets = prefixlen/8;
120 memset(addr, 0, sizeof(addr));
121 memmove(&addr[octets], sr.base, 16 - octets);
122 mask = 0xff >> (prefixlen % 8);
123 addr[octets] &= mask;
124 ar.base = addr;
125 ar.length = sizeof(addr);
126 RETERR(inet_totext(AF_INET6, &ar, target));
127 isc_region_consume(&sr, 16 - octets);
128 }
129
130 if (prefixlen == 0)
131 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
132
133 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
134 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
135 dns_name_init(&prefix, NULL);
136 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &sr);
137 sub = name_prefix(&name, tctx->origin, &prefix);
138 return (dns_name_totext(&prefix, sub, target));
139}

141static inline isc_result_t
142fromwire_in_a6(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
143 isc_region_t sr;
144 unsigned char prefixlen;
145 unsigned char octets;
146 unsigned char mask;
147 dns_name_t name;
148
149 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_a6);
150 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
151
152 UNUSED(type);
153 UNUSED(rdclass);
154
155 dns_decompress_setmethods(dctx, DNS_COMPRESS_NONE);
156
157 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &sr);
158 /*
159 * Prefix length.
160 */
161 if (sr.length < 1)
162 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
163 prefixlen = sr.base[0];
164 if (prefixlen > 128)
165 return (ISC_R_RANGE);
166 isc_region_consume(&sr, 1);
167 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, &prefixlen, 1));
168 isc_buffer_forward(source, 1);
169
170 /*
171 * Suffix.
172 */
173 if (prefixlen != 128) {
174 octets = 16 - prefixlen / 8;
175 if (sr.length < octets)
176 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
177 mask = 0xff >> (prefixlen % 8);
178 sr.base[0] &= mask; /* Ensure pad bits are zero. */
179 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, octets));
180 isc_buffer_forward(source, octets);
181 }
182
183 if (prefixlen == 0)
184 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
185
186 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
187 return (dns_name_fromwire(&name, source, dctx, options, target));
188}

190static inline isc_result_t
191towire_in_a6(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
192 isc_region_t sr;
193 dns_name_t name;
194 dns_offsets_t offsets;
195 unsigned char prefixlen;
196 unsigned char octets;
197
198 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_a6);
199 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
200 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
201
202 dns_compress_setmethods(cctx, DNS_COMPRESS_NONE);
203 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
204 prefixlen = sr.base[0];
205 INSIST(prefixlen <= 128);
206
207 octets = 1 + 16 - prefixlen / 8;
208 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, octets));
209 isc_region_consume(&sr, octets);
210
211 if (prefixlen == 0)
212 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
213
214 dns_name_init(&name, offsets);
215 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &sr);
216 return (dns_name_towire(&name, cctx, target));
217}

219static inline int
220compare_in_a6(ARGS_COMPARE) {
221 int order;
222 unsigned char prefixlen1, prefixlen2;
223 unsigned char octets;
224 dns_name_t name1;
225 dns_name_t name2;
226 isc_region_t region1;
227 isc_region_t region2;
228
229 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
230 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
231 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_a6);
232 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
233 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
234 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
235
236 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &region1);
237 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &region2);
238 prefixlen1 = region1.base[0];
239 prefixlen2 = region2.base[0];
240 isc_region_consume(&region1, 1);
241 isc_region_consume(&region2, 1);
242 if (prefixlen1 < prefixlen2)
243 return (-1);
244 else if (prefixlen1 > prefixlen2)
245 return (1);
246 /*
247 * Prefix lengths are equal.
248 */
249 octets = 16 - prefixlen1 / 8;
250
251 if (octets > 0) {
252 order = memcmp(region1.base, region2.base, octets);
253 if (order < 0)
254 return (-1);
255 else if (order > 0)
256 return (1);
257 /*
258 * Address suffixes are equal.
259 */
260 if (prefixlen1 == 0)
261 return (order);
262 isc_region_consume(&region1, octets);
263 isc_region_consume(&region2, octets);
264 }
265
266 dns_name_init(&name1, NULL);
267 dns_name_init(&name2, NULL);
268 dns_name_fromregion(&name1, &region1);
269 dns_name_fromregion(&name2, &region2);
270 return (dns_name_rdatacompare(&name1, &name2));
271}

273static inline isc_result_t
274fromstruct_in_a6(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
275 dns_rdata_in_a6_t *a6 = source;
276 isc_region_t region;
277 int octets;
278 uint8_t bits;
279 uint8_t first;
280 uint8_t mask;
281
282 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_a6);
283 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
284 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
285 REQUIRE(a6->common.rdtype == type);
286 REQUIRE(a6->common.rdclass == rdclass);
287
288 UNUSED(type);
289 UNUSED(rdclass);
290
291 if (a6->prefixlen > 128)
292 return (ISC_R_RANGE);
293
294 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(a6->prefixlen, target));
295
296 /* Suffix */
297 if (a6->prefixlen != 128) {
298 octets = 16 - a6->prefixlen / 8;
299 bits = a6->prefixlen % 8;
300 if (bits != 0) {
301 mask = 0xffU >> bits;
302 first = a6->in6_addr.s6_addr[16 - octets] & mask;
303 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(first, target));
304 octets--;
305 }
306 if (octets > 0)
307 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target,
308 a6->in6_addr.s6_addr + 16 - octets,
309 octets));
310 }
311
312 if (a6->prefixlen == 0)
313 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
314 dns_name_toregion(&a6->prefix, &region);
315 return (isc_buffer_copyregion(target, &region));
316}
317
318static inline isc_result_t
319tostruct_in_a6(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
320 dns_rdata_in_a6_t *a6 = target;
321 unsigned char octets;
322 dns_name_t name;
323 isc_region_t r;
324
325 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_a6);
326 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
327 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
328 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
329
330 a6->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
331 a6->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
332 ISC_LINK_INIT(&a6->common, link);
333
334 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
335
336 a6->prefixlen = uint8_fromregion(&r);
337 isc_region_consume(&r, 1);
338 memset(a6->in6_addr.s6_addr, 0, sizeof(a6->in6_addr.s6_addr));
339
340 /*
341 * Suffix.
342 */
343 if (a6->prefixlen != 128) {
344 octets = 16 - a6->prefixlen / 8;
345 INSIST(r.length >= octets);
346 memmove(a6->in6_addr.s6_addr + 16 - octets, r.base, octets);
347 isc_region_consume(&r, octets);
348 }
349
350 /*
351 * Prefix.
352 */
353 dns_name_init(&a6->prefix, NULL);
354 if (a6->prefixlen != 0) {
355 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
356 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &r);
357 RETERR(name_duporclone(&name, mctx, &a6->prefix));
358 }
359 a6->mctx = mctx;
360 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
361}
362
363static inline void
364freestruct_in_a6(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
365 dns_rdata_in_a6_t *a6 = source;
366
367 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
368 REQUIRE(a6->common.rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
369 REQUIRE(a6->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_a6);
370
371 if (a6->mctx == NULL)
372 return;
373
374 if (dns_name_dynamic(&a6->prefix))
375 dns_name_free(&a6->prefix, a6->mctx);
376 a6->mctx = NULL;
377}

379static inline isc_result_t
380additionaldata_in_a6(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
381 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_a6);
382 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
383
384 UNUSED(rdata);
385 UNUSED(add);
386 UNUSED(arg);
387
388 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
389}

391static inline isc_result_t
392digest_in_a6(ARGS_DIGEST) {
393 isc_region_t r1, r2;
394 unsigned char prefixlen, octets;
395 isc_result_t result;
396 dns_name_t name;
397
398 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_a6);
399 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
400
401 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r1);
402 r2 = r1;
403 prefixlen = r1.base[0];
404 octets = 1 + 16 - prefixlen / 8;
405
406 r1.length = octets;
407 result = (digest)(arg, &r1);
408 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
409 return (result);
410 if (prefixlen == 0)
411 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
412
413 isc_region_consume(&r2, octets);
414 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
415 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &r2);
416 return (dns_name_digest(&name, digest, arg));
417}

419static inline bool
420checkowner_in_a6(ARGS_CHECKOWNER) {
421
422 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_a6);
423 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
424
425 UNUSED(type);
426 UNUSED(rdclass);
427
428 return (dns_name_ishostname(name, wildcard));
429}
430
431static inline bool
432checknames_in_a6(ARGS_CHECKNAMES) {
433 isc_region_t region;
434 dns_name_t name;
435 unsigned int prefixlen;
436
437 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_a6);
438 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
439
440 UNUSED(owner);
441
442 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
443 prefixlen = uint8_fromregion(&region);
444 if (prefixlen == 0)
445 return (true);
446 isc_region_consume(&region, 1 + 16 - prefixlen / 8);
447 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
448 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
449 if (!dns_name_ishostname(&name, false)) {
450 if (bad != NULL)
451 dns_name_clone(&name, bad);
452 return (false);
453 }
454 return (true);
455}

457static inline int
458casecompare_in_a6(ARGS_COMPARE) {
459 return (compare_in_a6(rdata1, rdata2));
460}
